title: I need to get names, addresses and phone numbers from a website
snippet: I need to get names, addresses and phone numbers from www.gosection8.com  Enter "Los Angeles County, Ca" > search. All Property Types > click "House" AND "Townhouse/Villa" click search. Click each listing and grab address. Click "View Phone Number" grab name and phone. Put all in excel with headers Name, Phone, Address, City, State, Zip Code.  Do the same for "Orange County, Ca", "Riverside County, Ca" and "San Bernardino County, Ca"
